labels are a way to group kubernetes objects 


metadata:
      name:
      labels:
          color: blue
          
 kubectl get po --selector color=bue
 
 annotations are required to get additional meta-info about the resource
 
 metadata:
       name:
       labels:
           color: blue
           size: large
       annotations:
              buildVersion: 1.34
              
 
